er 16, 1996) is a Japanese actor, model, and former singer. He is best known for playing the role of the pink-haired Yuri Kyohei in the 2019 romantic comedy drama A Story to Read When You First Fall in Love, as well as Hikari Nonomura (ToQ 4gou) in the 2014 Super Sentai TV series Ressha Sentai ToQger.","name":"Ryusei Yokohama","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"橫濱流星","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"横浜流星","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Rjúsei Jokohama","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ryusei Yokohama","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"ריוסיי יוקוהמה","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BD","iso_639_1":"bn","name":"বাংলা","english_name":"Bengali","data":{"biography":"","name":"রিউসেই ইয়োকোহামা","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"ریوسي یوکوهاما","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"橫濱流星","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"ریوسی یوکوهاما","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"ml","name":"","english_name":"Malayalam","data":{"biography":"","name":"റ്യൂസെയ് യോകോഹാമ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"요코하마 류세이","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Рюсэй Ёкохама","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Рюсей Йокохама","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yokohama Ryusei","primary":false}}]}},"person_2592839_translations":{"at":1774211288625,"data":{"id":2592839,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Safia Grace Oakley-Green (born June 2001) is an English actress. She won a British Independent Film Award and a Scottish BAFTA for her performance in the horror film Out of Darkness (2022). She was named a 2023 Screen International Star of Tomorrow\n\nOakley-Green was born in Southwark, London before moving to Derbyshire. She trained at the Television Workshop in Nottingham. As of 2023, she was studying psychology at university.\n\nIn 2021, she appeared in the horror short film Requiem alongside fellow Television Workshop alumna Bella Ramsey. The short picked up increased attention after Ramsey's performance in the HBO television series The Last of Us raised her profile.\n\nOakley-Green made her feature film debut in the 2021 biopic The Colour Room for Sky Cinema alongside Phoebe Dynevor. She made her television debut as Cinderella Jackson in the 2022 BBC One crime drama Sherwood. Also in 2022, she starred in the Scottish caveman horror Out of Darkness, previously entitled The Origin, for which she received the British Independent Film Award for Breakthrough Performance in December 2022. She later also given the best film actress award by BAFTA Scotland for the role.\n\nIn 2023, Oakley-Green had a recurring role as Andy in the first series of Disney+ comedy Extraordinary. She has roles in the second series of The Lazarus Project on Sky Max and the Paramount+ series The Burning Girls.","name":"Safia Oakley-Green","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сафія Оклі-Ґрін","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сафия Окли-Грин","primary":false}}]}},"person_67979_translations":{"at":1774211290551,"data":{"id":67979,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Michael Eklund is a Canadian film and television actor. He's a graduate from the Alberta College of Art and Design, Calgary, Canada.","name":"Michael Eklund","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"迈克尔·艾克朗德（Michael Eklund）是加拿大电影和电视演员。他毕业于加拿大卡尔加里的阿尔伯塔艺术与设计学院。","name":"迈克尔·艾克朗德","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Майкл Екланд","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Майкл Эклунд","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"邁克爾·艾克朗德（Michael Eklund）是加拿大電影和電視演員。他畢業於加拿大卡爾加里的阿爾伯塔藝術與設計學院。","name":"邁克爾·艾克朗德","primary":false}}]}},"person_237455_translations":{"at":1774211291347,"data":{"id":237455,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Samuel George Claflin (born 27 June, 1986) is an English actor. After graduating from the London Academy of Music and Dramatic Art in 2009, he began his acting career on television and had his first film role as Philip Swift in Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides (2011).\n\nClaflin gained wider recognition for playing Finnick Odair in The Hunger Games film series (2013–2015) and for his starring role in the romantic comedy Me Before You (2016). He has since portrayed Oswald Mosley in the television series Peaky Blinders (2019–2022) and Mycroft Holmes in the mystery film Enola Holmes (2020). In 2023, Claflin played Billy Dunne in Daisy Jones & The Six. Based on the book of the same name, it follows the story of a rock band in the 1970s, and premiered on Amazon Prime Video on March 3, 2023.","name":"Sam Claflin","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сэм Клафлин","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Samuel „Sam“ George Claflin (* 27. Juni 1986 in Ipswich, Suffolk, England) ist ein britischer Schauspieler.\n\nSein Schauspieldebüt hatte er in dem Fernsehmehrteiler Die Säulen der Erde als Richard von Shiring. In dem vierten Teil der Fluch-der-Karibik-Reihe, Pirates of the Caribbean – Fremde Gezeiten, spielt er in einer Nebenrolle den Missionar Philip. Im Fußballdrama United, das sich mit dem Wiederaufbau der Mannschaft nach dem Flugzeugunglück des Manchester United Teams 1958 befasst, spielt er die Rolle des Duncan Edwards. 2012 spielte er die Rolle eines Prinzen in einer amerikanischen Neuverfilmung des Märchens Schneewittchen, Snow White and the Huntsman, der am 31. Mai 2012 in die deutschen Kinos kam. In dem 2013 erschienenen Science-Fiction-Film Die Tribute von Panem – Catching Fire übernahm Claflin die Rolle des Finnick Odair. Es folgte die Hauptrolle des Bryan McNeil im Horror-Thriller The Quiet Ones sowie die Hauptrolle des Alex Stewart in der romantischen Komödie Love, Rosie – Für immer vielleicht, die auf dem gleichnamigen Roman von Cecelia Ahern basiert. Im Jahr 2016 spielte er im Film Ein ganzes halbes Jahr die männliche Hauptrolle des Will Trainor, neben Emilia Clarke und Charles Dance. Der Film basiert auf dem gleichnamigen Roman von Jojo Moyes.\n\nQuelle: Wikipedia","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"Urodził się w 1986 roku w Ipswich, Anglia. Uczęszczał do Costessey High School w Norwich. Jako mały chłopiec był wielkim fanem piłki nożnej i przejawiał niemały talent do gry. W wieku 16 lat, po dwukrotnym złamaniu kostki, zmuszony był zrezygnować z pasji. Do aktorstwa zachęcił go nauczyciel z liceum, zobaczywszy jego występ w szkolnym przedstawieniu. W 2003 roku podjął studia sztuki scenicznej w Norwich City College, by niedługo później przenieść się do słynnej London Academy of Music and Dramatic Art.  Na małym ekranie debiutował w 2010 roku drugoplanową rolą w \"Filarach Ziemi\", równocześnie pojawił się również w \"Any Human Heart\". Już w kwietniu tego samego roku udało mu się dostać angaż w hollywoodziej kontynuacji przebojowej serii \"Piraci z Karaibów: Na nieznanych wodach\". Zanim megaprodukcja debiutowała w kinach, można było oglądać go w roli piłkarza Duncana Edwardsa w telewizyjnym \"United\" wyprodukowanym dla BBC. Niedługo później został obsadzony w kolejnym blockbusterze - \"Królewnie Śnieżce i Łowcy\". W sierpniu 2012 otrzymał angaż do drugiej części cyklu \"Igrzyska śmierci\"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"サム・クラフリン","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GE","iso_639_1":"ka","name":"ქართული","english_name":"Georgian","data":{"biography":"","name":"სემ კლაფლინი","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"샘 클라플린","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"山姆·克萊弗林","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"塞缪尔·乔治·克拉夫林（Samuel George Claflin，1986年6月27日-），英国演员。2009年从伦敦音乐与戏剧艺术学院毕业后，他在电视上开始了他的演艺生涯，并在《加勒比海盗：陌生潮汐》（2011）中饰演菲利普·斯威夫特（Philip Swift）。\n\n克拉夫林因在《饥饿游戏》系列电影（2013-2015）中扮演芬尼克·奥代尔以及在浪漫喜剧《在你面前》（2016）中担任主演而获得更广泛的认可。此后，他在电视连续剧《Peaky Blinders》（2019-2022 年）中饰演奥斯瓦尔德·莫斯利，在悬疑电影《伊诺拉·福尔摩斯》（2020 年）中饰演迈克罗夫特·福尔摩斯。2023年，克拉夫林在《黛西·琼斯与六人组》中饰演比利·邓恩。根据同名书籍改编，讲述了 1970 年代摇滚乐队的故事，并于 2023 年 3 月 3 日在亚马逊 Prime Video 首播。","name":"山姆·克拉弗林","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сем Клафлін","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"NL","iso_639_1":"nl","name":"Nederlands","english_name":"Dutch","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RS","iso_639_1":"sr","name":"Srpski","english_name":"Serbian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сем Клафлин","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"سام کلافلین","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"แซมคลอฟลิน","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MK","iso_639_1":"mk","name":"","english_name":"Macedonian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сем Клафлин","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"סם קלאפלין","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SG","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"山姆·克拉弗林","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BD","iso_639_1":"bn","name":"বাংলা","english_name":"Bengali","data":{"biography":"","name":"স্যাম ক্ল্যাফলিন","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"塞繆爾·喬治·克拉夫林（Samuel George Claflin，1986 年 6 月 27 日-），英國演員。2009 年從倫敦音樂與戲劇藝術學院畢業後，他在電視上開始了他的演藝生涯，並在《加勒比海盜：陌生潮汐》（2011）中飾演菲利普·斯威夫特（Philip Swift）。\n\n克拉夫林因在《飢餓遊戲》系列電影（2013 - 2015）中扮演芬尼克·奧代爾以及在浪漫喜劇《在你面前》（2016）中擔任主演而獲得更廣泛的認可。此後，他在電視聯續劇《Peaky Blinders》（2019 - 2022 年）中飾演奧斯瓦爾德·莫斯利，在懸疑電影《伊諾拉·福爾摩斯》（2020 年）中飾演邁克羅夫特·福爾摩斯。2023 年，克拉夫林在《黛西·瓊斯與六人組》中飾演比利·鄧恩。根據同名書籍改編，講述了 1970 年代搖滾樂隊的故事，並於 2023 年 3 月 3 日在亞馬遜 Prime Video 首播。","name":"森加芬","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HY","iso_639_1":"hy","name":"","english_name":"Armenian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Սեմ Քլաֆլին","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BY","iso_639_1":"be","name":"беларуская мова","english_name":"Belarusian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сэм Клафлін","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"سام كلافلن","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Σαμ Κλάφλιν","primary":false}}]}},"person_4613664_translations":{"at":1774211307462,"data":{"id":4613664,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Braden McCawley","primary":true}}]}},"person_2104285_translations":{"at":1774211312378,"data":{"id":2104285,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Han Hae-in","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"한해인","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Han Hae-in","primary":false}}]}},"person_2762135_translations":{"at":1774211317338,"data":{"id":2762135,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Vivienne Tien is a Chinese-Americ